description:
Nils Bars discovered that e2fsprogs incorrectly handled certain file
systems. A local attacker could use this issue with a crafted file
system image to possibly execute arbitrary code.
title: e2fsprogs vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary:
e2fsprogs could be made to crash or possibly run programs if it processed
a specially crafted file system image.
